    dc:description "Figure 1. Stenotanais leonardoi sp. nov. A. Holotype, neuter (MZUSP 43545), lateral view; B. Paratype, male (MZUSP 43546), lateral view; C. Paratype, juvenile (MZUSP 43563), dorsal view. Scale bars: 1.0 mm." ;
